Duskull (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0354: Banette
Pokémon
#0356: Dusclops →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Duskull (TCG Pocket).

Duskull has been featured on 18 different cards since it debuted in the EX Sandstorm expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Duskull cards are normally Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Duskull

Duskull
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
